{"lemma":"ظَفِرَةٍ","slug":"ظَفِرَةٍ","root":"ظ.ف.ر","root_slug":"ظ-ف-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ظ-ف-ر","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"ظَفِر","root":"ظفر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":8},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n27563","n27572","n27573"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B8%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%90%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"fingernail"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"claw","examples":[{"text":"وَعَلَى الَّذِينَ هَادُوا حَرَّمْنَا كُلَّ ذِي ظُفُرٍ","english":"We forbade every animal with undivided hoofs"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to triumph over, to win, to superate"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to win, to gain, to receive","examples":[{"text":"مَنْ صَبَرَ ظَفِرَ","english":"Patience is victory (literally: he who is patient, wins.)"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make victorious; to grant victory; to aid"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of ظَفِرَ (ẓafira) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"obtainment, success, victory"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"level ground"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Proto-Semitic *θ̣upr-, *θ̣ipr- (“nail, claw”). Cognate with Akkadian 𒌢 (ṣuprum) and Biblical Hebrew צִפֹּרֶן (ṣippórɛn)."},"ipa":["/ðˤufr/","/ðˤu.fur/","/ðˤa.fi.ra/","/ðˤaf.fa.ra/","/ðˤa.far/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27563","headword_ar":"ظَفَرَهُ","root":"Zfr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 2.       -A2-  [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZafarN","text_ar":"ظَفَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2- ]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zafirato","text_ar":"ظَفِرَتْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eayonuhu","text_ar":"عَيْنُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, O, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZafarN","text_ar":"ظَفَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZafaArapN","text_ar":"ظَفَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (O;) and, as some say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zufirat","text_ar":"ظُفِرَت"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His eye had what is termed a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zafarap","text_ar":"ظَفَرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zufor","text_ar":"ظُفْر"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T, S, O, K.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zufira","text_ar":"ظُفِرَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had upon his eye what is termed a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zafarap","text_ar":"ظَفَرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zufor","text_ar":"ظُفْر"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T, O, K.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zafira","text_ar":"ظَفِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZafarN","text_ar":"ظَفَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He attained, got, got possession of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acquired, what he desired,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sough:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, * S, * M, * A, * Msb, K: *) he"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"succeeded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was successful:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he won, was victorious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gained the victory:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiZ~afara","text_ar":"اِظَّفَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiZotafara","text_ar":"اِظْتَفَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zafira","text_ar":"ظَفِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zafira bihi","text_ar":"ظَفِرَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zafirahu","text_ar":"ظَفِرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He attained it, got it, got possession of it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acquired it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) and in like manner ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiZ~afara","text_ar":"اِظَّفَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AifotaEala","text_ar":"اِفْتَعَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zafirotu biAlD~aAl~api","text_ar":"ظَفِرْتُ بِالضَّالَّةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I found the stray,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lost beast."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zafira biEaduw~ihi","text_ar":"ظَفِرَ بِعَدُوِّهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Akh, S, A,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zafirahu","text_ar":"ظَفِرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gained the victory,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mastery, over his enemy; he overcame him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * A, Msb. *) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zafirati Aln~aAqapu laqaHFA","text_ar":"ظَفِرَتِ النَّاقَةُ لَقَحًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The she-camel took,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"received, impregnation."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA Zafiratoka EayoniY","text_ar":"مَا ظَفِرَتْكَ عَيْنِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, T, S, A, K)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muno*u HiynK","text_ar":"مُنْذُ حِينٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, T) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muno*u zamaAnKi","text_ar":"مُنْذُ زَمَانٍِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"My eye hath not seen thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for some time"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (AZ, T, S, A, K:) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^axa*atoka","text_ar":"مَا اَخَذَتْكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (AZ, T.)       -A4-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zafara","text_ar":"ظَفَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the dial. of Himyer is said by Freytag, on the authority of the Kitáb el-Addád, to signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sat."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":["T","S","O","K","Msb","Lth","A","Akh","AZ"]},{"entry_id":"n27572","headword_ar":"ظُفْرَةٌ","root":"Zfr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain plant, burning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"biting, to the tongue,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zufor","text_ar":"ظُفْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nail"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in its coming forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has a beneficial effect upon foul ulcers, and warts."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zuforapu AlEajuwzi","text_ar":"ظُفْرَةُ العَجُوزِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The rounded head of prickles of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thistle called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasak","text_ar":"حَسَك"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, * TA.) ―         -b3-  See also the next paragraph."}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n27573","headword_ar":"ظَفَرَةٌ","root":"Zfr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A pellicle that comes over the eye,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, Mgh, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"growing from the side next the nose,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the white of the eye,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extending to the black:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) sometimes it is cut off: if left, it covers the eye, and obscures the sight: (T:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain disease in the eye, which causes a tegument like the nail to come over it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece of flesh that grows at the inner angle of the eye, extending to the black, and sometimes encroaching upon the black:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) it is also called ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZuforN","text_ar":"ظُفْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A 'Obeyd, T, S, M, Mgh, O, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZuforapN","text_ar":"ظُفْرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, Mgh,) these two terms being applied to it by the physicians, (Mgh,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZafarN","text_ar":"ظَفَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZifaArapN","text_ar":"ظِفَارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in a copy of the T, as on the authority of Ibn-Buzurj,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZafaArapN","text_ar":"ظَفَارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (So in the O.)"}],"source_refs":["T","S","Mgh","O","K","M","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}